{"word":"G3975 - παχύνω - pachýnō - pakh-oo'-no - Wax gross","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παχύνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pachýnō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pakh-oo'-no</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Wax gross</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கொழுத்திரு"},{"paragraph":"to make thick; to make fat, to fatten"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a derivative of <a href=\"#/G4078 - πήγνυμι - pḗgnymi - payg'-noo-mee/4078\">G4078</a> (meaning <i>thick</i>); to <i>thicken</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>fatten</i> (figuratively <i>stupefy</i> or <i>render callous</i>): - wax gross.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3975/3975\">G3975</a>, <a href=\"#/G4456/4456\">G4456</a>, <a href=\"#/G4457/4457\">G4457</a>"}]}